These are Puzzles for 7x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-2-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, hot-chocolate, milk, sprite
There are 4 different nationalities: spanish, polish, indonesian, australian
4 different games are played: backgammon, chess, poker, monopoly
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, havana, oliveros, baccarat
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, goldfish, hedgehog, lizard
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, baseball, lacrosse, sailing
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: orchid, daffodil, daisy, tulip
 1. the spanish is between the person drinking fanta and the owner of the chinchilla##2
 2. the indonesian is on the far left##1
 3. the person who growstulip is on the left of the vegafina-smoker##1
 4. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
 5. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 6. the polish is on the right of the person playing chess##1
 7. the havana-smoker is between the person who growsdaffodil and the owner of the lizard##2
 8. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
 9. the australian is the vegafina-smoker##1
10. the person who's sport is baseball is the polish##1
11. the person who's sport is sailing is the person playing poker##1
12. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
13. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
14. the australian is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
15. the oliveros-smoker is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Beverage      | milk        | sprite     | hot-chocolate | fanta      |
| Nationality          | indonesian | polish    | spanish      | australian  |
| Game         | chess  | monopoly    | backgammon       | poker     |
| Cigar   | oliveros        | baccarat       | havana          | vegafina |
| Pet           | hedgehog    | chinchilla | goldfish      | lizard     |
| Sport         | badminton   | baseball   | lacrosse      | sailing    |
| Flower     | orchid        | daffodil        | tulip    | daisy    |

