 4. the colonial house is the owner of the fish##1
 5. the person who growssunflower is the person eating radish##1
 6. the craftsman house is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
 7. the owner of the cat is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
 8. the person eating cherry is the person driving the bike##1
 9. the person driving the airplane is the person playing poker##1
10. the person eating blueberry is on the right of the australian##1
11. the person playing billiard is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
12. the person eating blueberry is between the person driving the roller and the person eating cucumber##2
13. the person who growsiris is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
14. the townhouse house is on the left of the australian##1
15. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person eating radish##1

.:: Answer ::.
